 ```

### Brand Creation

This endpoint allows the creation of a new brand.

#### Request Body

- `name` (required | string) - The name of the brand.

- `image` (nullable | image) - The image file for the brand.


#### Response

The response for this request follows the JSON schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "image_url": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

