# Update Category

This endpoint allows the user to update a specific category by making an HTTP PUT request to {{site_seller}}/category/15.

### Request Body

- type (text, required): Type of the category. Example: post/product

- name (text, required): Name of the category.


### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object conforming to the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  }
}

 ```

The response object contains a status and message property to indicate the status of the request.

### Get Product Reviews

This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve the reviews for a specific product.

#### Request

The request should include the following parameter:

- `product_id` (query parameter): The ID of the product for which the reviews are to be retrieved.


#### Response

The response will be a JSON object following the schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "reviews": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "review_id": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "rating": {
            "type": "number"
          },
          "comment": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

